OL,3,CTower demolition delayed as officials
OL,4,Cwork out how to do it safely
OL,6,FThe demolition of a derelict Newcastle
OL,7,Ftower block has been delayed.
OL,9,FNewcastle City Council has pushed back
OL,10,Fplans to blow up the empty Hexham
OL,11,FHouse, in Walker.
OL,13,FThe 16-storey housing block was
OL,14,Fexpected to be brought down by the end
OL,15,Fof May in a controlled explosion,
OL,16,Fwhich would be the first of its kind
OL,17,Fin Newcastle since 2008.
