OL,3,CTower demolition delayed as officials
OL,4,Cwork out how to do it safely
OL,6,FThe demolition is yet to take place
OL,7,Fand no new date has been set, with
OL,8,Fcivic centre officials saying that
OL,9,Fthey are still working out how to
OL,10,Fsafely carry out the blast.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Newcastle City
OL,13,FCouncil confirmed: "Plans for the
OL,14,Fdemolition of Hexham House are
OL,15,Fprogressing but, as with any work of
OL,16,Fthis type, safety must be a primary
OL,17,Fconcern. We are currently consulting
OL,18,Fwith local stakeholders and service
OL,19,Fproviders to make sure the demolition
OL,20,Fis completed safely and efficiently.
