OL,6,F"We recently held an information day
OL,7,Fwith local residents to identify any
OL,8,Fsupport we may need to put in place on
OL,9,Fdemolition day. We will confirm the
OL,10,Fdate of the demolition once it is
OL,11,Fagreed."
OL,13,FHexham House's former neighbour, Titan
OL,14,FHouse, was pulled down last year in a
OL,15,Fgradual process that saw "nibbling
OL,16,Fmachines" used to remove the block.
