OL,6,FThe city council said in March that
OL,7,Fthere had been "concerns" arising from
OL,8,Fthat process and that a controlled
OL,9,Fexplosion was now deemed the safest
OL,10,Foption for the second tower.
OL,12,FPlans to get rid of the two blocks
OL,13,Fhave been in the works for years and
OL,14,Fhave suffered multiple setbacks `
OL,15,Fincluding when, in 2022, officials
OL,16,Fwarned that work to remove asbestos
OL,17,Ffrom the empty sites has been "made
OL,18,Fmore challenging" after a gang of
OL,19,Fthieves broke in to steal copper
OL,20,Fpiping.
