OL,6,FThe clearance works, which will also
OL,7,Finclude a block of low-rise flats over
OL,8,Fthe nearby Church Walk shops being
OL,9,Fdemolished, will eventually pave the
OL,10,Fway for up to 50 new homes to be built
OL,11,Fon the Church Street site.
OL,13,FThe last explosive demolition in
OL,14,FNewcastle was in 2008 when Sir Bobby
OL,15,FRobson pushed the button to reduce the
OL,16,Fold Scottish and Newcastle Brewery to
OL,17,Frubble.
